- As a member of the organisation, I would like to view all the countries in a continent organised by largest population to smallest to aid me in my research work.
- As a researcher, I want to be able to see the number of people who speak certain languages including the percentage of the world population, to see which are more prevelant.
- As a data analyst, I would like to be able to look at the population of people living in cities, and people not living in cities in each country, so that I can analyse population density.
- As an employee, I want to input a value for N and receive a list of the top N populated countries in the world, so that I can focus on certain countries.
- As an anaylst, I would like to have access to the population of all the continents, so that I can use it when comparing figures.
